---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
	<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
		  <img src="https://cdn4.iconfinder.com/data/icons/logos-and-brands/512/356_Vaadin_logo-1024.png" alt="Vaadin Logo" width="48" height="48" />
		  <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/spring-logo.png" alt="Spring-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
		</div>
		<h2>Informatics Engineer | Senior Full-Stack Java Specialist</h2>
		<div class="expertise-content">
			<p class="lead">Enterprise-grade solutions with:</p>
			<ul class="tech-highlights">
				<li>
					<strong>Vaadin 24</strong> - 28+ production deployments handling 50K+ daily users
					<span class="tech-tag">Type-Safe UIs</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Spring Boot 3</strong> - Microservices with 99.98% uptime SLA
					<span class="tech-tag">Cloud Native</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>AI Integration</strong> - NLP-powered document processing (70% efficiency gain)
					<span class="tech-tag">OpenAI API</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="metrics">
				<div class="metric">
					<span class="number">10+</span>
					<span class="label">Years Experience</span>
				</div>
				<div class="metric">
					<span class="number">40K+</span>
					<span class="label">Daily Users</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="globe" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Technical Localization Lead</h2>
		<ul class="tech-highlights">
			<li>Localized 5 Vaadin apps for EMEA/APAC markets using i18n best practices, ensuring linguistic and cultural precision.</li>
			<li>Provided precise translations of JavaDoc and technical specifications across English, Spanish, and French, ensuring consistency and clarity.</li>
			<li>Achieved an 80% reduction in UI translation bugs by designing and deploying custom L10n test automation frameworks.</li>
		</ul>
		<div class="metrics">
			<div class="metric">
				<span class="number">5</span>
				<span class="label">Languages</span>
			</div>
			<div class="metric">
				<span class="number">30+</span>
				<span class="label">Localized Projects</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluency/48/java-coffee-cup-logo.png" alt="Java Logo" width="48" height="48" />
		<h2>Java Architecture</h2>
		<ul class="tech-highlights">
			<li>CI/CD Pipeline Optimization : Engineered seamless Vaadin app deployments via GitLab-AWS integration, minimizing manual intervention and maximizing release efficiency.</li>
			<li>Engineered scalable systems with integrated monitoring (Micrometer & Prometheus) to optimize JVM performance</li>
			<li>Delivered high-quality, robust architectures aligned with modern DevSecOps practices.</li>
		</ul>
		<div class="metrics">
			<div class="metric">
				<span class="number">200+</span>
				<span class="label">Prod Deploys/Yr</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>



<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.metrics {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: flex-start; /* align left */
		align-items: center;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap; /* ensures responsiveness on smaller screens */
	}

	.metric {
		background: var(--gray-900);
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		text-align: center;
		min-width: 120px;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
		flex: 0 0 auto; /* prevent stretching */
	}

	.metric:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
	}

	.metric .number {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--accent-regular, #6366f1);
	}

	.metric .label {
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--gray-400);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}


	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>